---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contacto">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-12 bg-stone-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl text-stone-800 mb-4">Contacto</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-600 max-w-2xl">
        Estamos aquí para ayudarte. Contacta con nosotros para reservas o información.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-800 mb-6">Información de contacto</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Dirección</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">C/ Real 10<br>40174 Valleruela de Pedraza<br>Segovia, Castilla y León, España</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Teléfono</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">+34 685 19 92 72<br>+34 921 53 37 59</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Email</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">info@mirinconcillo.com</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800">Registro</h3>
                <p class="text-stone-600">Turismo CRA 40/385</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-stone-200">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-4">Síguenos</h3>
            <div class="flex gap-4">
              <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Mi-Rinconcillo/271047946302174" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 bg-stone-100 hover:bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-stone-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC97toWpXCp69dx4ue5f3aMw" target="_blank" class="w-10 h-10 bg-stone-100 hover:bg-amber-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-stone-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M23.498 6.186a3.016 3.016 0 0 0-2.122-2.136C19.505 3.545 12 3.545 12 3.545s-7.505 0-9.377.505A3.017 3.017 0 0 0 .502 6.186C0 8.07 0 12 0 12s0 3.93.502 5.814a3.016 3.016 0 0 0 2.122 2.136c1.871.505 9.376.505 9.376.505s7.505 0 9.377-.505a3.015 3.015 0 0 0 2.122-2.136C24 15.93 24 12 24 12s0-3.93-.502-5.814zM9.545 15.568V8.432L15.818 12l-6.273 3.568z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-800 mb-6">Cómo llegar</h2>
          
          <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-4">Desde Madrid - Opción 1</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mb-4">
              <strong>A1 - Burgos</strong>: Desvío en el km 99 en Santo Tomé del Puerto, por la N-110 hacia Segovia. En Arcones, dirección Pedraza, hacia La Velilla. Desde La Velilla, dirección Sepúlveda (SG-P 2322), 4,5 km.
            </p>
            <a href="https://maps.google.es/maps?f=d&source=s_d&saddr=Madrid&daddr=Calle+Real,+40174+Valleruela+de+Pedraza" target="_blank" class="text-amber-700 hover:text-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
              </svg>
              Abrir en Google Maps
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-stone-800 mb-4">Desde Madrid - Opción 2</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm mb-4">
              <strong>A6 - A Coruña</strong>: Tomar la SG-20 antes de Segovia y salir por la N-110 hacia Soria. Pasando La Salceda, desviarse a Sepúlveda hasta La Velilla. Desde La Velilla, dirección Sepúlveda (SG-P 2322), 4,5 km.
            </p>
            <a href="https://maps.google.es/maps?f=d&source=s_d&saddr=Madrid&daddr=40.644178,-4.033356+to:Calle+Real,+40174+Valleruela+de+Pedraza" target="_blank" class="text-amber-700 hover:text-amber-800 text-sm font-semibold flex items-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"/>
              </svg>
              Abrir en Google Maps
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-amber-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-amber-200">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-2">Reservas</h3>
            <p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">
              También puedes reservar a través de Booking.com
            </p>
            <a href="http://www.booking.com/hotel/es/mi-rinconcillo-pedraza.es.html" target="_blank" class="inline-block mt-3 bg-amber-700 hover:bg-amber-800 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded text-sm transition-colors">
              Reservar en Booking
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
